      "title": "Prohibition in Colombo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Pudukadai Court has imposed this restraining order as it is believed that the protestors are ready to pitch a tent and continue to stay on the road in front of Olkot Mawatha under Purakottai Police Division - Sri Pothirukarama Viharai.",
        "According to this, the convener of the 'Surakimu Lanka' national movement, Hon. Bahiangala Ananda Sagara Thera, President of Teacher-Principals Union Hon. Ulapane Sumangala Thera and founder of Bhumi Mata Manusath Foundation Kalupovila Paduma Thera have been banned from visiting the said places. (a)"
